<D>__{his highness has not yet taken a wife.}
<C>__{willie}
<P>__{(happily)}
<D>__{no? well, i guess he just hasn't met the right woman...}
<A>__{as willie chatters on with the prime minister, indiana wanders off. he moves to a wall where bronze statues and strange devo tional objects are displayed.}
<C>__{capt. blumburtt}
<P>__{(joining indy)}
<D>__{interested in local curios?}
