<D>__{there are no stories anymore.}
<C>__{indiana}
<D>__{well, i don't know... we came here from a small village and the peas ants there told us that the pankot palace was growing powerful again becuase of some ancient evil.}
<A>__{indiana smiles and shrugs.}
